    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I also encountered the same issue in the current stable 1.1.0 version. It seems that the total width is fixed at a maximum of 1200 px instead of adapting to the full width of the browser window. This regression is annoying for many users with monitors that have a larger resolution. \n\nAt first glance it might be connected to \"notebook-container\", this div is set in the CSS here to 1170px instead of the full width. \n"
